channel.title: Energy Rail Pistol(with alter version edited a bit)
channel.description: Took me an hour Amy (mostly the color..i just couldn't come up with a decent scheme) I made it with the idea of a self generating ammunition that is deprived by consumed energy hence no mag is present. Please if you don't like or think something is off tell me. Dont bother commenting on the scheme because no matter what i tried i had no idea what kind of scheme could or would go with this model. I also posted WIREFRAMES (go crazy -.-) And please don't bother criticizing my knowledge of a handguns anatomical structure. i posted two versions because some people prefer others

item.title: Energy Rail Pistol(with alter version edited a bit)
item.dc:creator: @amy_webb1 amy_webb
item.description:
@amy_webb1 wrote:

I’m not a fan of guns personally, so i don’t have as much criticism as you might like.

Maybe just find a theme you’re a bit more into, something that you could explore further? You said you couldn’t find one, and it is usually a problem with modelling. Try looking around the internet, thinking of animals, historical events, fantasy, just something to get the juices flowing. Just not as impressed as i thought i’d be with your next one, my fault for a disinterest in this (others enjoy it as seen in the comments).
